snippet.title: Tales of Symphonia Remastered | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Build new alliances and try out different unison attacks to defeat your fiercest enemies across Sylvarant.

Tales of Symphonia Remastered releases February 17, for PS4, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch!
